org.jscripter.emu.java.lang
Class String

java.lang.Object
  org.jscripter.emu.java.lang.String
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.CharSequence, Serializable, Comparable<String>
public final class String
extends java.lang.Object
implements Comparable<String>, java.lang.CharSequence, Serializable

Internally represents character strings, emulating a standard java.lang interface or class with the same simple name as this one.

This interface or class is only used internally by JS re-compiler implementations.

Please refer to the Java API Standards for detail description of the original class or interface.

Author:
J.J.Liu (Jianjun Liu) at http://www.jscripter.org
JavaScript:
Re-compilers must redirect the resolution of the emulated original Java class or interface to this one.
